trans-unit.source: Represents the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures"></xref> or <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragments"></xref> element of an <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument"></xref>.
This class has no public constructor.

References to an XpsStructure are obtained through the <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IDocumentStructureProvider.AddDocumentStructure%2A> or <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IStoryFragmentProvider.AddStoryFragment%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: XpsStructure에 대 한 참조를 통해 가져온는 <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IDocumentStructureProvider.AddDocumentStructure%2A>또는 <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IStoryFragmentProvider.AddStoryFragment%2A>메서드.</xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IStoryFragmentProvider.AddStoryFragment%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IDocumentStructureProvider.AddDocumentStructure%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information about the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures> or <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragments> elements of an <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument>, see Chapter 9 in the *XPS Paper Specification (XPS)* which you can download at [http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=65761](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=65761).
trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 자세한 내용은 <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures>또는 <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragments>의 요소는 <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument>에서 9 장 참조는 *XPS XPS Paper Specification ()* 에서 다운로드할 수 있는 [http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=65761](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=65761).</xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragments> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures>
